# Decentralized DB

This application demonstrates how to add users' info to a decentralized database using Node.js and orbited through  IPFS.

## Installation

Clone the [repo](https://github.com/emmanueletukudo/doinggud) `cd` Doingud and run the command below to start the server.

```bash
npm i
```

## Usage
A request to the `http://localhost/9000` will return a hardcoded user with the info. below:

```bash
Emmanuel Etukudo
```

## Contributing
There is room for more implementations example authenticating the user and displaying their details.
